---
import GlossaryEntry from '../../layouts/GlossaryEntry.astro';
---
<GlossaryEntry
  category="Electronic Component"
  title="Decoupling Capacitor"
  subtitle="100uF electrolytic - power supply"
  backTo="/guides/pam8403-esp32-audio#cap-decoupling"
  backLabel="Back to PAM8403 guide"
  highlights={[
    'Value: 100uF electrolytic',
    'Polarity matters - + leg to PAM8403 VCC',
    '- leg to GND',
    'Mount as close to the PAM8403 as possible',
    'Smooths power-supply noise from audio bursts',
  ]}
>
  <svg slot="svg" viewBox="0 0 240 260" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;max-width:180px;display:block;margin:auto">
    <ellipse cx="120" cy="60" rx="52" ry="15" fill="#3a5a3a" stroke="#5a8a5a" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    <rect x="68" y="60" width="104" height="110" fill="#3a5a3a" stroke="#5a8a5a" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    <ellipse cx="120" cy="170" rx="52" ry="15" fill="#2e4e2e" stroke="#5a8a5a" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    <text x="120" y="58" fill="#e8a020" font-size="18" font-family="monospace" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="bold">+</text>
    <text x="120" y="94" fill="#ccc" font-size="9" font-family="monospace" text-anchor="middle">100uF</text>
    <line x1="100" y1="170" x2="100" y2="230" stroke="#ccc" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
    <line x1="140" y1="170" x2="140" y2="220" stroke="#ccc" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
    <text x="100" y="248" fill="#e8a020" font-size="13" font-family="monospace" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="bold">+</text>
    <text x="140" y="238" fill="#888" font-size="13" font-family="monospace" text-anchor="middle">-</text>
  </svg>
  <Fragment slot="desc">
    <p>A decoupling capacitor sits across a power rail to absorb sudden current spikes.</p>
    <p>When the PAM8403 plays a loud sound it draws a burst of current from the 5V line. Without this cap, that spike causes a tiny voltage drop which comes out as hiss or noise through the speaker. The cap provides instant local current, keeping the supply stable.</p>
  </Fragment>
</GlossaryEntry>
